<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="aink351">
<l>attap palaviṉ veyiṟiṉ ciṟukā</l>
<l>yaruñcurañ celvō raruntiṉar kaḻiyuṅ</l>
<l>kāṭupiṉ ṉoḻiya vantaṉar tīrkiṉip</l>
<l>pallita ḻuṇkaṇ maṭantainiṉ</l>
<l>nalleḻi lalkul vāṭiya nilaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>[He] has returned, leaving the wilderness behind him, </l>
<l>where in the difficult desert travellers suffer feeding </l>
<l>on small sun-eaten fruits of the roadside jackfruit trees. </l>
<l>O young girl with eyes like many-petaled flowers</l> 
<l>[darkened] with collyrium! </l>
<l>May this state end, when your good beautiful hips are fading!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
